title: Negro Leagues Baseball Museum president to speak on campus Oct. 21 (Ohio University)
text: ( Source : Ohio University ) Oct 13 , 2015 From staff reports Bob Kendrick , president of the Negro Leagues Baseball Museum in Kansas City , will present,' How Negro Leagues Baseball Shaped Civil Rights in America ,' at 7 p.m. Wednesday, Oct. 21
